Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:30.00,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&H2D85FF&\pos(950,950)\fsp30}翻译：弥禾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:49.22,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\1c&HB0E4FF&\pos(1000,850)\fsp70}家园卫士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:57.30,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA5D5F1&\pos(1650,1020)}解说\N{\fs30}大卫·爱登堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:39.56,中文,,0,0,0,,(低无线电干扰)\N{\rEng}LOW RADIO CHATTER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:45.04,中文,,0,0,0,,大卫·爱登堡:这些人在打猎\N{\rEng}DAVID ATTENBOROUGH: These people are hunting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:48.20,中文,,0,0,0,,地球上最濒危的动物之一.\N{\rEng}for one of the most endangered animals on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:03.92,中文,,0,0,0,,黑犀牛--一种因角而被偷猎的动物.\N{\rEng}The black rhino - an animal poached for its horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:06.04,中文,,0,0,0,,(枪声)\N{\rEng}GUN FIRES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.00,中文,,0,0,0,,但他们不会伤害她。\N{\rEng}But they aren't going to harm her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:20.24,中文,,0,0,0,,杜米·兹瓦内 (Dumi Zwane) 和他的团队正在执行救援任务。\N{\rEng}Dumi Zwane and his team are on a rescue mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:24.44,中文,,0,0,0,,杜米:我想我永远不会停止为犀牛而战。\N{\rEng}DUMI: I don't think I'll ever stop fighting for rhino.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:26.52,中文,,0,0,0,,这是不可能的。\N{\rEng}It's just not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:28.00,中文,,0,0,0,,好的！ 是的...\N{\rEng}OK! Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:32.08,中文,,0,0,0,,他们正在一个安全的避风港建立一个新的繁殖群。\N{\rEng}They're setting up a new breeding colony in a safe haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:33.68,中文,,0,0,0,,让她穿两件。\N{\rEng}Get her on two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.68,0:01:35.76,中文,,0,0,0,,二。 好的。 那挺好的。\N{\rEng}Two. OK. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:39.56,中文,,0,0,0,,这位女性将处于这一切的中心。\N{\rEng}This female is going to be at the very centre of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.76,中文,,0,0,0,,她的体重有一吨多...\N{\rEng}She weighs over a tonne...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:47.04,中文,,0,0,0,,去！\N{\rEng}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:49.56,中文,,0,0,0,,……只有一种方法可以让她出去。\N{\rEng}..and there's only one way to get her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.00,中文,,0,0,0,,就是这样。\N{\rEng}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我们到了。 完美的！\N{\rEng}There we are. Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:09.04,中文,,0,0,0,,当我看着它飞走的时候，我的心情非常激动。\N{\rEng}When I watch it fly off, it's very emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.92,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一种美好的感觉。\N{\rEng}It's a beautiful feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:21.56,中文,,0,0,0,,她已经服用了镇静剂并且很安全......\N{\rEng}She is sedated and safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.96,中文,,0,0,0,,......不到半小时，她就会回到地面\N{\rEng}...and in less than half an hour, she'll be back on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:33.40,中文,,0,0,0,,并在一个可以拯救她整个物种的项目中开始新的生活，\N{\rEng}and starting a new life in a project that could save her entire species,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:37.44,中文,,0,0,0,,感谢杜米和他出色的团队。\N{\rEng}thanks to Dumi and his remarkable team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:55.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我们开始制作第一个《地球脉动》系列\N{\rEng}We started making the very first Planet Earth series
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.92,中文,,0,0,0,,就在20多年前。\N{\rEng}just over 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:02.08,中文,,0,0,0,,从那时起，我们的摄影团队在世界各地进行拍摄\N{\rEng}Since then, our camera teams have filmed all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:06.56,中文,,0,0,0,,并参观了一些最荒凉、最偏远的角落。\N{\rEng}and visited some of its wildest and most remote corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:16.48,中文,,0,0,0,,但事实是我们拍摄的大多数动物\N{\rEng}But the truth is that most of the animals we filmed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:21.28,中文,,0,0,0,,在过去的二十年里，现在比以前更加罕见了。\N{\rEng}over these last two decades are now rarer than they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.16,中文,,0,0,0,,以及他们居住的地方\N{\rEng}And the places where they live
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.24,中文,,0,0,0,,面临更大的破坏危险。\N{\rEng}are in greater danger of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:31.52,中文,,0,0,0,,但那些年我看到了另一个变化\N{\rEng}But I've seen another change in those years,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.68,中文,,0,0,0,,一个充满希望的改变。\N{\rEng}a hopeful change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:37.20,中文,,0,0,0,,新一代杰出人士正在挺身而出\N{\rEng}A new generation of remarkable people are stepping up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.20,中文,,0,0,0,,拯救野生动物。\N{\rEng}to save wildlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.44,中文,,0,0,0,,他们正在克服巨大的障碍，\N{\rEng}They're overcoming huge obstacles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.60,中文,,0,0,0,,去危险的地方旅行，\N{\rEng}travelling to dangerous places,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.00,中文,,0,0,0,,有时甚至冒着生命危险。\N{\rEng}and sometimes even risking their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.20,中文,,0,0,0,,对我来说，他们是真正的英雄。\N{\rEng}To me, they are true heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.52,中文,,0,0,0,,这是其中一些人的故事。\N{\rEng}This is the story of some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:05.04,中文,,0,0,0,,隐藏在安第斯山脉的中心\N{\rEng}Hidden in the heart of the Andes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:08.64,中文,,0,0,0,,是 Centro Jambatu 研究中心。\N{\rEng}is the Centro Jambatu research centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.68,中文,,0,0,0,,它保护的是，也许令人惊讶的是，\N{\rEng}It's protecting members of what is, perhaps surprisingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:19.44,中文,,0,0,0,,世界上最濒临灭绝的动物群。\N{\rEng}the most endangered group of animals in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.92,中文,,0,0,0,,青蛙。\N{\rEng}Frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:29.88,中文,,0,0,0,,这些个体是其特定物种的最后一个。\N{\rEng}These individuals are the very last of their particular species.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.16,中文,,0,0,0,,他们被带到这里不仅是为了保护，\N{\rEng}They're brought here not only for protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:37.68,中文,,0,0,0,,但更重要的是，\N{\rEng}but, more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.44,中文,,0,0,0,,来增加他们的数量。\N{\rEng}to increase their numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.00,中文,,0,0,0,,还有找到他们的人...\N{\rEng}And the person to find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:46.40,中文,,0,0,0,,..海梅·库莱布拉斯。\N{\rEng}..Jaime Culebras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我七岁时第一次看到青蛙\N{\rEng}I was seven the first time that I saw a frog
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:55.32,中文,,0,0,0,,改变了我的生活。\N{\rEng}and just changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.92,中文,,0,0,0,,而且从他小时候起，\N{\rEng}And ever since his childhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:01.48,中文,,0,0,0,,他一直在探索最偏远的地方\N{\rEng}he's been exploring the remotest places
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:04.32,中文,,0,0,0,,并寻找最稀有的青蛙。\N{\rEng}and searching for the rarest frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.04,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一只叶蛙。\N{\rEng}This is a leaf frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.44,中文,,0,0,0,,他真是太棒了。\N{\rEng}He is just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:18.24,中文,,0,0,0,,不可能不爱上这样的动物，不是吗？\N{\rEng}It's impossible to don't fall in love with an animal like this, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:26.68,中文,,0,0,0,,但这里有一只非常特别的青蛙。\N{\rEng}But there is one frog here that is very special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:32.88,中文,,0,0,0,,他的名字是悲伤的圣地亚哥。\N{\rEng}His name, Sad Santiago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.92,中文,,0,0,0,,这是悲伤的圣地亚哥。\N{\rEng}This is Sad Santiago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:39.28,中文,,0,0,0,,他很伤心，因为他孤身一人。\N{\rEng}He's sad because he's alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:43.92,中文,,0,0,0,,他是该物种最后的成员之一。\N{\rEng}He's one of the last members of his species.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.52,中文,,0,0,0,,而且他需要一个女性。\N{\rEng}And he needs a female.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:53.08,中文,,0,0,0,,被称为莫罗纳-圣地亚哥丑角蛙，\N{\rEng}Known as the Morona-Santiago harlequin frog,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:57.00,中文,,0,0,0,,他可能是世界上最稀有的青蛙。\N{\rEng}he may be the rarest frog in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.92,中文,,0,0,0,,当这里的其他青蛙正在尽力而为时\N{\rEng}While the other frogs here are doing their best
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.72,中文,,0,0,0,,为了增加他们的人口，\N{\rEng}to increase their populations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:11.20,中文,,0,0,0,,圣地亚哥已经独自坐了四年了。\N{\rEng}Santiago has sat alone for four long years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:15.88,中文,,0,0,0,,也许它不是最美丽的青蛙，但他值得被爱。\N{\rEng}Maybe it's not the most beautiful frog, but he deserves love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.88,中文,,0,0,0,,圣地亚哥现在已经老了，\N{\rEng}Santiago has now grown old,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.88,中文,,0,0,0,,如果詹姆不能很快找到一个女人给他，\N{\rEng}and if Jaime can't find a female for him soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.56,中文,,0,0,0,,整个物种可能会灭绝。\N{\rEng}the whole species could become extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.16,中文,,0,0,0,,雷霆隆隆\N{\rEng}THUNDER RUMBLES
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:34.84,中文,,0,0,0,,最后一次看到这些青蛙的地方......\N{\rEng}The last place where one of these frogs was seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:42.24,中文,,0,0,0,,..在厄瓜多尔云雾森林的一座高山上。\N{\rEng}..was high up on a mountain in the cloud forest of Ecuador.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.72,中文,,0,0,0,,只有一种方法可以到达那里。\N{\rEng}There's only one way to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:54.28,中文,,0,0,0,,驴子喷鼻息\N{\rEng}DONKEY SNORTS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:08.76,中文,,0,0,0,,加入他行列的是青蛙猎人达尔文\N{\rEng}Joining him is fellow frog-hunter Darwin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:12.96,中文,,0,0,0,,还有海梅的搭档兼青蛙科学家弗朗西斯卡。\N{\rEng}and Jaime's partner and frog scientist, Francesca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.52,中文,,0,0,0,,哦！\N{\rEng}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.08,中文,,0,0,0,,来吧，瓦马诺斯。\N{\rEng}Come on, vamanos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.36,中文,,0,0,0,,阿里巴。\N{\rEng}Arriba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.32,中文,,0,0,0,,弗朗西斯卡:这是地球上最潮湿的地方之一，\N{\rEng}FRANCESCA: This is one of the wettest places on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:34.16,中文,,0,0,0,,现在实际上是雨季，雨季，\N{\rEng}and right now it's actually the wet season, the rainy season,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.24,中文,,0,0,0,,所以雨下得更大了。\N{\rEng}so it rains even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:39.56,中文,,0,0,0,,浑身湿透，还爬满了虫子……\N{\rEng}Soaking wet and teeming with bugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.00,中文,,0,0,0,,..对于青蛙来说，这是一个完美的地方。\N{\rEng}..it's a perfect place for frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我们走吧。\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:49.08,中文,,0,0,0,,大多数青蛙都会在晚上从躲藏处出来。\N{\rEng}Most frogs come out of hiding at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:56.24,中文,,0,0,0,,这个地方非常美妙。\N{\rEng}This place is extremely wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:08:00.52,中文,,0,0,0,,但你必须小心你的手放在哪里。\N{\rEng}But you have to be careful where you put your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.40,中文,,0,0,0,,和他在一起就是...\N{\rEng}Being with him is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.00,中文,,0,0,0,,..这很不寻常。\N{\rEng}..it's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,这不是你们之间的正常关系。\N{\rEng}It's not your regular relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.56,中文,,0,0,0,,她笑了\N{\rEng}SHE LAUGHS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:19.20,中文,,0,0,0,,哦，他着迷了。 他真的很着迷。\N{\rEng}Oh, he's obsessed. He's really obsessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:22.48,中文,,0,0,0,,像这样的溪流应该充满青蛙\N{\rEng}Streams like this should be full of frogs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.24,中文,,0,0,0,,许多不同物种的...\N{\rEng}of many different species...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.44,中文,,0,0,0,,..但他们搜查了一夜却一无所获。\N{\rEng}..but they search all night and find nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.32,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一片寂静的森林。\N{\rEng}It's a silent forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:42.16,中文,,0,0,0,,这是可悲的。\N{\rEng}It's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:53.72,中文,,0,0,0,,青蛙的声音正在慢慢从我们的世界消失。\N{\rEng}The sound of frogs is slowly disappearing from our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:09:00.44,中文,,0,0,0,,现在唯一可以找到多种青蛙的地方\N{\rEng}The only place many frog species can now be found
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.00,中文,,0,0,0,,在博物馆里。\N{\rEng}is in a museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:11.92,中文,,0,0,0,,一个关键原因是一种叫做壶菌的真菌的传播......\N{\rEng}A key reason is the spread of a fungus called chytrid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.96,中文,,0,0,0,,..可以在青蛙潮湿的皮肤上生长，\N{\rEng}..that can grow on the moist skins of frogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.76,中文,,0,0,0,,最终杀死他们。\N{\rEng}eventually killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:23.84,中文,,0,0,0,,据信有 90 个物种因此灭绝，\N{\rEng}90 species are thought to have become extinct as a consequence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:27.96,中文,,0,0,0,,目前还有近 600 种濒临灭绝的物种。\N{\rEng}and almost 600 more are now critically endangered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:36.64,中文,,0,0,0,,在壶菌出现之前，我很确定你可以走路\N{\rEng}Before chytrid, I'm pretty sure that you could walk
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:40.72,中文,,0,0,0,,穿过溪流，到处可见\N{\rEng}through the stream and see everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:45.20,中文,,0,0,0,,岩石上有很多很多青蛙，\N{\rEng}many, many, many frogs on the rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:48.08,中文,,0,0,0,,呼叫“呜呜呜”！\N{\rEng}calling   prrr-prrr  !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:57.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望我是在青蛙病爆发之前出生的。\N{\rEng}I wish I had been born before the frog disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.64,中文,,0,0,0,,一夜又一夜...\N{\rEng}Night after night...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.16,中文,,0,0,0,,..他们搜索流。\N{\rEng}..they search the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.92,中文,,0,0,0,,海梅！\N{\rEng}Jaime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.80,中文,,0,0,0,,终于有一个发现了。\N{\rEng}At last, there is a discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:26.32,中文,,0,0,0,,声音是一...\N{\rEng}The sound is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:26.32,中文,,0,0,0,,杰米·特里尔斯\N{\rEng}JAIME TRILLS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道具体在哪里，但或多或??少就在那里。\N{\rEng}I don't know exactly where, but it's there, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.16,中文,,0,0,0,,在水中！\N{\rEng}En el agua!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我们有它。\N{\rEng}We have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.76,中文,,0,0,0,,一只玻璃青蛙。\N{\rEng}A glass frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.16,中文,,0,0,0,,一只非常漂亮的玻璃青蛙。\N{\rEng}A really beautiful glass frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:46.28,中文,,0,0,0,,玻璃蛙变得越来越稀有，\N{\rEng}Glass frogs are becoming increasingly rare,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:48.92,中文,,0,0,0,,有一天，它们也可能消失。\N{\rEng}and one day they, too, could disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.92,中文,,0,0,0,,但这不是他们想要的。\N{\rEng}But it's not what they are looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:59.40,中文,,0,0,0,,事实是无数的物种灭绝了......\N{\rEng}The fact is that countless species go extinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.76,中文,,0,0,0,,..未被注意到。\N{\rEng}..unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:07.72,中文,,0,0,0,,海梅能做的就是继续他的寻找\N{\rEng}All Jaime can do is to continue his search
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.12,中文,,0,0,0,,为圣地亚哥找个伴侣。\N{\rEng}for a mate for Santiago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.36,中文,,0,0,0,,在那里？\N{\rEng}It's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:30.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我发现了一个女的！\N{\rEng}I found a female!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:35.60,中文,,0,0,0,,啊啊！\N{\rEng}Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:38.52,中文,,0,0,0,,呜呼！\N{\rEng}Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.48,中文,,0,0,0,,是个女的！ 看。\N{\rEng}It's a female! Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:48.24,中文,,0,0,0,,体型比雄性大。\N{\rEng}The size is bigger than the males.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.08,中文,,0,0,0,,哇。\N{\rEng}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我很高兴！\N{\rEng}I feel so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:55.64,中文,,0,0,0,,第一女！\N{\rEng}The first female!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:01.24,中文,,0,0,0,,她可能成为新育种计划的基石。\N{\rEng}She could be the cornerstone of a new breeding programme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:05.32,中文,,0,0,0,,圣地亚哥会非常非常非常非常高兴。\N{\rEng}Santiago will be very, very, very, very, very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.96,中文,,0,0,0,,詹姆笑了\N{\rEng}JAIME LAUGHS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.32,中文,,0,0,0,,因为她真的很美！\N{\rEng}Because she's really beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我的手中，充满了希望。\N{\rEng}In my hand, I have hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我有这个物种的救星，\N{\rEng}I have the saviour of this species,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.92,中文,,0,0,0,,用于育种计划和人们繁殖它。\N{\rEng}for breeding programmes and for people to reproduce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:22.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道，好像我手里还抱有希望。\N{\rEng}I don't know, it's like I just have hope in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:30.24,中文,,0,0,0,,世界上有7000多种青蛙，\N{\rEng}There are over 7,000 species of frogs in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.28,中文,,0,0,0,,你可能会问...\N{\rEng}and you may well ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:36.80,中文,,0,0,0,,..如果有一些灭绝了，真的很重要吗？\N{\rEng}..does it really matter if a few go extinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:45.56,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧，看看这个微小的物种\N{\rEng}Well, just look at this tiny species
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.80,中文,,0,0,0,,的毒箭蛙。\N{\rEng}of poison arrow frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.56,中文,,0,0,0,,科学家在它的皮肤上发现了一种化学物质......\N{\rEng}Scientists discovered a chemical on its skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:58.44,中文,,0,0,0,,..比吗啡强200倍。\N{\rEng}..200 times stronger than morphine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:06.68,中文,,0,0,0,,现在他们正在研究如何创造强大的新型止痛药。\N{\rEng}Now they are studying how it works to create powerful new painkillers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:16.16,中文,,0,0,0,,但自然世界不仅仅是一个巨大的药箱。\N{\rEng}But the natural world is not just one vast medicine chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.68,中文,,0,0,0,,远不止于此。\N{\rEng}It's far more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:21.60,中文,,0,0,0,,它是我们的生命维持系统，\N{\rEng}It is our life support system,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:25.16,中文,,0,0,0,,将我们的世界凝聚在一起的织物。\N{\rEng}the fabric that holds our world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:28.56,中文,,0,0,0,,移除它的一部分，一个物种或一个栖息地，\N{\rEng}Remove a part of it, a species or a habitat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:31.48,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道会发生什么。\N{\rEng}and there's no knowing what could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:34.88,中文,,0,0,0,,低沉的隆隆声\N{\rEng}LOW RUMBLING
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.76,中文,,0,0,0,,一个典型的例子是森林象。\N{\rEng}A prime example is the forest elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:44.20,中文,,0,0,0,,他们在维护方面发挥着至关重要的作用\N{\rEng}They play a crucial role in maintaining
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.28,中文,,0,0,0,,非洲的雨林...\N{\rEng}the rainforests of Africa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.64,中文,,0,0,0,,大象喇叭\N{\rEng}ELEPHANT TRUMPETS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:51.16,中文,,0,0,0,,..撒播种子并清理空地\N{\rEng}..dispersing seeds and making clearings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:54.12,中文,,0,0,0,,然后被许多其他动物使用。\N{\rEng}that are then used by many other animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:06.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我们在 2004 年拍摄了这些照片\N{\rEng}We filmed these images in 2004
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.96,中文,,0,0,0,,第一部《地球脉动》系列。\N{\rEng}for the first Planet Earth series.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:09.96,中文,,0,0,0,,大象喇叭\N{\rEng}ELEPHANT TRUMPETS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:14.80,中文,,0,0,0,,九年后，偷猎者来到这里\N{\rEng}Nine years later, poachers came here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.40,中文,,0,0,0,,并为了象牙而杀死了26头大象......\N{\rEng}and killed 26 elephants for their ivory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:23.16,中文,,0,0,0,,..包括四头小牛。\N{\rEng}..including four of the calves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:31.28,中文,,0,0,0,,自从第一个系列以来，\N{\rEng}Since that first series,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:33.96,中文,,0,0,0,,非洲森林象的数量\N{\rEng}the number of forest elephants across Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:36.32,中文,,0,0,0,,已经下降了三分之二。\N{\rEng}has dropped by two-thirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:45.92,中文,,0,0,0,,但制止屠杀是一件危险的事情。\N{\rEng}But stopping the slaughter is a risky business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:53.48,中文,,0,0,0,,阿比让，西非科特迪瓦...\N{\rEng}Abidjan, in Cote d'Ivoire, West Africa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:59.80,中文,,0,0,0,,..全球非法象牙贸易网络的一部分。\N{\rEng}..part of the global network in the illegal ivory trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:11.44,中文,,0,0,0,,一个陌生人从越南飞来，\N{\rEng}A stranger has flown in from Vietnam,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:14.20,中文,,0,0,0,,象牙进口中心。\N{\rEng}a hub for the import of ivory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:36.84,中文,,0,0,0,,她的名字是--Trang Nguyen。\N{\rEng}Her name - Trang Nguyen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:43.16,中文,,0,0,0,,她的专长--渗透非法野生动物贸易\N{\rEng}Her speciality - infiltrating the illegal wildlife trade
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.96,中文,,0,0,0,,冒充买家。\N{\rEng}by posing as a buyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:22.52,中文,,0,0,0,,Trang 正在与一个名为 EAGLE 的自然资源保护主义者网络合作。\N{\rEng}Trang is working with a network of conservationists called EAGLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:26.88,中文,,0,0,0,,她的联系人是 Rens Ilgen。\N{\rEng}Her contact here is Rens Ilgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:33.08,中文,,0,0,0,,但西非这一新贸易的特别之处在于，\N{\rEng}But what is particular with this new trade in West Africa is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.80,中文,,0,0,0,,正如你所看到的，很多象牙都来自小象。\N{\rEng}as you can see, a lot of the tusks are from baby elephants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.92,中文,,0,0,0,,所以，他们真的只剩下最后一头大象了。\N{\rEng}So, they're really down to the last elephants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:43.60,中文,,0,0,0,,上周，有七人死亡。\N{\rEng}Last week, seven people were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.08,中文,,0,0,0,,七游侠被杀？\N{\rEng}Seven ranger was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:47.28,中文,,0,0,0,,所以，很明显，这不仅仅是象牙贸易的问题，\N{\rEng}So, clearly, it is not just about the ivory trade,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.44,中文,,0,0,0,,但很多人，护林员，也被杀害。\N{\rEng}but a lot of people, rangers, that are being killed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.24,中文,,0,0,0,,这是……这是战争。 这是战争。\N{\rEng}It's...it's war. It's war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.24,中文,,0,0,0,,他们甚至还去寻找小象。 是的。\N{\rEng}And they're even going for the baby elephants. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.56,中文,,0,0,0,,现在，Trang 已经确定了她的任务。\N{\rEng}Now Trang is set her task.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:03.40,中文,,0,0,0,,所以，我想让你见见象牙教父。\N{\rEng}So, I want you to meet the godfather of ivory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我们四年前就已经逮捕了他\N{\rEng}We already arrested him four years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.12,中文,,0,0,0,,当他拥有400公斤象牙时，\N{\rEng}when he had 400kg of ivory,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.52,中文,,0,0,0,,他向越南社区提供的\N{\rEng}which he was supplying to the Vietnamese community
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:13.48,中文,,0,0,0,,与越南黑手党有联系。\N{\rEng}linked to the Vietnamese mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:18.20,中文,,0,0,0,,由于他以前被捕过，所以他可能会非常谨慎。\N{\rEng}As he has been arrested before, he might be very cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.96,中文,,0,0,0,,这可能很危险。\N{\rEng}It might be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:25.32,中文,,0,0,0,,她准备伪装成一名女商人--\N{\rEng}She prepares her disguise as a businesswoman -
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.80,中文,,0,0,0,,但在她的夹克下面，\N{\rEng}but under her jacket,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.68,中文,,0,0,0,,隐藏的录音设备。\N{\rEng}hidden recording equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.64,中文,,0,0,0,,EAGLE 的卧底特工一直在跟踪\N{\rEng}EAGLE's undercover agents have been following
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.64,中文,,0,0,0,,教父多年。\N{\rEng}the godfather for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.88,中文,,0,0,0,,现在是抓住他的时候了。\N{\rEng}Now is the moment to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.68,中文,,0,0,0,,这是你们第一次见面。\N{\rEng}This is your first meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:54.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你们只是要讨论并互相了解。\N{\rEng}You're just going to discuss and get to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:56.60,中文,,0,0,0,,看看他们有没有产品。 确切地。\N{\rEng}See if they have the products. Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我要进去，\N{\rEng}I'm going in,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:02.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要背对门坐着，\N{\rEng}and I need to sit facing away from the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.76,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我不想让别人看到我和他在一起。\N{\rEng}because I don't want people to see me with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:08.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就在附近...是的。\N{\rEng}We will be close by... Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:10.68,中文,,0,0,0,,..并且不会出错。\N{\rEng}..and nothing will go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.36,中文,,0,0,0,,好的。\N{\rEng}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:16.04,中文,,0,0,0,,祝你好运。\N{\rEng}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.36,中文,,0,0,0,,再见。\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:28.56,中文,,0,0,0,,她在当地的一家咖啡馆遇见了教父。\N{\rEng}She meets the godfather at a local cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.76,中文,,0,0,0,,秘密摄像机捕捉到了这个故事。\N{\rEng}The secret cameras capture the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:49.56,中文,,0,0,0,,庄:嗯嗯。\N{\rEng}TRANG: Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:14.04,中文,,0,0,0,,但教父否认有任何象牙可供出售。\N{\rEng}But the godfather denies having any ivory for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.68,中文,,0,0,0,,庄:谢谢。\N{\rEng}TRANG: Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:32.08,中文,,0,0,0,,耶耶耶。\N{\rEng}Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:33.48,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢。\N{\rEng}Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.32,中文,,0,0,0,,也许没有象牙。\N{\rEng}Perhaps there's no ivory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:40.24,中文,,0,0,0,,或者也许他不信任Trang。\N{\rEng}Or maybe he doesn't trust Trang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.60,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个严重的挫折。\N{\rEng}It's a serious setback.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:53.16,中文,,0,0,0,,但还有其他交易者。\N{\rEng}But there are other traders out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:57.20,中文,,0,0,0,,也许她出现在城里会吸引他们。\N{\rEng}Perhaps her presence in town will draw them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:03.08,中文,,0,0,0,,过去的每一天，\N{\rEng}Every day that passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:05.92,中文,,0,0,0,,更多的大象被杀死。\N{\rEng}more elephants are killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.88,中文,,0,0,0,,对于 Trang 来说，这部作品非常个人化。\N{\rEng}For Trang, this work is very personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.68,中文,,0,0,0,,当我23岁的时候，我接到了电话。\N{\rEng}When I was 23, I got the phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:31.96,中文,,0,0,0,,医生告诉我，我患有肠癌。\N{\rEng}The doctor told me that I had bowel cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:36.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我脑子里第一个闪现的就是我还年轻\N{\rEng}The first thing pop up in my mind is that I'm so young,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:38.20,中文,,0,0,0,,那么，我怎么会得癌症呢？\N{\rEng}well, how can I get cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.28,中文,,0,0,0,,一旦患上癌症，\N{\rEng}Once you have cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你不知道自己还能活多久\N{\rEng}you don't know how long you're going to live for,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:48.24,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我想做任何事，那么我现在就应该做。\N{\rEng}and if I want to do anything, then I should just do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:52.16,中文,,0,0,0,,就在那时我说:“好吧，我要做卧底”\N{\rEng}And that's when I said,   OK, I'm just going to do undercover,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:54.32,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我不知道我什么时候会死。\N{\rEng}because I don't know when I'm going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:57.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我还不如做一些真正有意义的事情。\N{\rEng}I might as well do something really meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:07.88,中文,,0,0,0,,目前，Trang 处于缓解期。\N{\rEng}Currently, Trang is in remission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:18.00,中文,,0,0,0,,三天后，事情有了突破。\N{\rEng}Three days later, there's a breakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:21.44,中文,,0,0,0,,电话 PING\N{\rEng}PHONE PINGS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:25.40,中文,,0,0,0,,交易员发送的视频。\N{\rEng}A video sent by a trader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:31.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以看到这个视频有大约14、15颗象牙。\N{\rEng}I can see that this video have about 14, 15 ivory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:33.88,中文,,0,0,0,,它们是大象牙，也是小象牙。\N{\rEng}They are big tusks, they are also small tusks as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:36.24,中文,,0,0,0,,它显然来自小象。\N{\rEng}It's obviously come from baby elephants.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:37.92,中文,,0,0,0,,诱饵已经上钩了。\N{\rEng}The bait has been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.68,中文,,0,0,0,,Trang 和 EAGLE 团队必须迅速采取行动。\N{\rEng}Trang and the EAGLE team must act fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:51.24,中文,,0,0,0,,她要去实现新的目标。\N{\rEng}She goes to meet the new targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.08,中文,,0,0,0,,第一份工作...\N{\rEng}First job...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:57.16,中文,,0,0,0,,庄:晚安。\N{\rEng}TRANG: Bonsoir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:21:58.92,中文,,0,0,0,,..赢得他们的信任。\N{\rEng}..gain their trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:09.84,中文,,0,0,0,,干杯。\N{\rEng}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:10.92,中文,,0,0,0,,干杯。 干杯。\N{\rEng}Cheers. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:14.36,中文,,0,0,0,,庄说英语:\N{\rEng}TRANG SPEAKING ENGLISH:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.36,中文,,0,0,0,,交易员:好的。\N{\rEng}TRADER: OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:25.44,中文,,0,0,0,,最终，Trang 说服商人搬到\N{\rEng}Eventually, Trang persuades the traders to move to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:28.76,中文,,0,0,0,,附近的一个酒店房间...\N{\rEng}a hotel room nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:32.44,中文,,0,0,0,,..称量象牙并进行交易。\N{\rEng}..to weigh the ivory and make the transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:45.80,中文,,0,0,0,,庄:把门关上。 关门。\N{\rEng}TRANG: Close the door. Close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:03.96,中文,,0,0,0,,象牙按公斤出售。\N{\rEng}Ivory is sold by the kilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:05.92,中文,,0,0,0,,TRANG:刚刚超过20个。\N{\rEng}TRANG: That is just over 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:07.28,中文,,0,0,0,,20.2？\N{\rEng}20.2?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:08.76,中文,,0,0,0,,交易员:20.3。\N{\rEng}TRADER: 20.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:12.12,中文,,0,0,0,,为了这次运输，整个大象家族被杀。\N{\rEng}A whole elephant family was killed for this haul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.20,中文,,0,0,0,,低语气\N{\rEng}LOW CHATTER
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:18.00,中文,,0,0,0,,它的价值超过 5,000 英镑。\N{\rEng}It's worth over ?5,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:21.08,中文,,0,0,0,,在这里，这是一年的工资。\N{\rEng}Here, that is a year's salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:27.76,中文,,0,0,0,,交易者没有意识到的...\N{\rEng}What the traders don't realise...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:30.96,中文,,0,0,0,,..警察就在楼上的房间里吗？\N{\rEng}..is that the police are in the room above,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:33.80,中文,,0,0,0,,等待 Trang 的短信。\N{\rEng}waiting for a text from Trang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.12,0:23:46.44,中文,,0,0,0,,轻声:好吧，我们走吧。\N{\rEng}SOFTLY: OK, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.56,中文,,0,0,0,,耳语\N{\rEng}WHISPERING
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:01.20,中文,,0,0,0,,敲门\N{\rEng}KNOCK ON DOOR
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:02.68,中文,,0,0,0,,庄:谁在那儿？\N{\rEng}TRANG: Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:05.16,中文,,0,0,0,,服务？\N{\rEng}Service?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:14.68,中文,,0,0,0,,庄:你去开门吧。\N{\rEng}TRANG: You go open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:16.12,中文,,0,0,0,,交易员:好的。\N{\rEng}TRADER: OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.80,中文,,0,0,0,,安静地:把它放在这儿吧。\N{\rEng}QUIETLY: Just put it down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:22.20,中文,,0,0,0,,警察！ 警察！\N{\rEng}Police! Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.20,0:24:23.92,中文,,0,0,0,,庄尖叫\N{\rEng}TRANG SCREAMS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.92,0:24:25.84,中文,,0,0,0,,别动，别动，别动！\N{\rEng}Don't move, don't move, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:27.88,中文,,0,0,0,,庄尖叫\N{\rEng}TRANG SCREAMS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:39.96,中文,,0,0,0,,庄说法语:\N{\rEng}TRANG SPEAKING FRENCH:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.56,0:24:44.40,中文,,0,0,0,,为了她自己的安全，\N{\rEng}For her own safety,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.40,0:24:48.12,中文,,0,0,0,,她必须保留她的掩护故事并表现得像个罪犯......\N{\rEng}she has to keep her cover story and behave as a criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.12,0:24:50.00,中文,,0,0,0,,低声喊叫\N{\rEng}MUFFLED SHOUTING
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.12,0:24:56.04,中文,,0,0,0,,..这意味着她也必须被捕。\N{\rEng}..which means she must also be arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.04,0:24:59.04,中文,,0,0,0,,警方发布命令\N{\rEng}POLICE ISSUE ORDERS
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.04,0:25:09.64,中文,,0,0,0,,全球供应链中的一个环节...\N{\rEng}A link in the global supply chain...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.64,0:25:10.96,中文,,0,0,0,,..破碎的。\N{\rEng}..broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.12,0:25:22.44,中文,,0,0,0,,Trang被带走了，\N{\rEng}Trang is whisked away,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.44,0:25:25.88,中文,,0,0,0,,当商贩被带到警察局时，\N{\rEng}whilst the traders are taken to the police station,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.88,0:25:29.12,中文,,0,0,0,,没人知道她的参与。\N{\rEng}none the wiser about her involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:41.12,中文,,0,0,0,,明年，EAGLE 又抓获 140 名毒贩\N{\rEng}Over the next year, EAGLE catch 140 more traffickers
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.12,0:25:44.96,中文,,0,0,0,,打击全球野生动物贸易。\N{\rEng}in the fight against the global wildlife trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.52,0:25:50.96,中文,,0,0,0,,但对于Trang来说，这是她的最后一次手术。\N{\rEng}But for Trang, this is her last operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.28,0:25:55.88,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我们可以展示她的脸。\N{\rEng}It's why we can show her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.72,0:26:09.36,中文,,0,0,0,,对她来说，多待一分钟是不安全的。\N{\rEng}It's not safe for her to stay a minute longer than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.64,0:26:20.32,中文,,0,0,0,,Trang 的最终任务是从阿比让消失……\N{\rEng}Trang's final task is to vanish from Abidjan...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.32,0:26:22.28,中文,,0,0,0,,..永远。\N{\rEng}..for ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.08,0:26:35.48,中文,,0,0,0,,在世界各地，野生动物的数量正在惊人地下降。\N{\rEng}Across the world, the numbers of wild animals are falling alarmingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.48,0:26:37.80,中文,,0,0,0,,短短二十年--\N{\rEng}In just two decades -
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.80,0:26:40.96,中文,,0,0,0,,自从我们开始制作第一个《地球脉动》系列以来 -\N{\rEng}since we started making the first Planet Earth series -
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.96,0:26:44.64,中文,,0,0,0,,全球野生动物的数量已经减少，\N{\rEng}the abundance of wildlife around the globe has dropped,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.64,0:26:47.80,中文,,0,0,0,,平均而言，增幅超过30%。\N{\rEng}on average, by over 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.08,0:26:52.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我们正面临一场灾难，一场灾难。\N{\rEng}We're facing a disaster, a catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.60,0:26:58.16,中文,,0,0,0,,科学家称我们正处于大规模灭绝的边缘。\N{\rEng}Scientists say that we're on the edge of a mass extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.80,0:27:03.48,中文,,0,0,0,,这是由人类活动造成的。\N{\rEng}It's being caused by human activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.48,0:27:07.40,中文,,0,0,0,,所以人类也有能力阻止它。\N{\rEng}So humans also have the power to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.64,0:27:14.60,中文,,0,0,0,,即使拯救一个物种也需要具备多种品质。\N{\rEng}It takes many qualities to save even one species.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.88,0:27:18.48,中文,,0,0,0,,决心...\N{\rEng}Determination...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.16,0:27:22.92,中文,,0,0,0,,..勇气...\N{\rEng}..courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.48,0:27:26.36,中文,,0,0,0,,..和热情。\N{\rEng}..and passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.48,0:27:32.20,中文,,0,0,0,,通常，还需要另一种成分......\N{\rEng}And often, there's another ingredient that's needed...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.92,0:27:36.96,中文,,0,0,0,,..大胆思考的能力。\N{\rEng}..the ability to think big.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.68,0:27:46.40,中文,,0,0,0,,在维也纳，凯瑟琳娜·休克勒 (Katharina Huchler) 刚刚开始一份新工作。\N{\rEng}In Vienna, Katharina Huchler is just starting a new job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.40,0:27:48.36,中文,,0,0,0,,工资太可怕了。\N{\rEng}The pay is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.56,0:27:51.48,中文,,0,0,0,,时间很长。\N{\rEng}The hours are long.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.64,0:27:55.92,中文,,0,0,0,,而且没有休息日。\N{\rEng}And there are no days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.48,0:28:01.52,中文,,0,0,0,,她即将成为一名养母。\N{\rEng}She is about to become a foster mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.52,0:28:02.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你好。\N{\rEng}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.80,0:28:04.36,中文,,0,0,0,,你好。\N{\rEng}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.80,0:28:04.36,中文,,0,0,0,,吱吱声\N{\rEng}CHEEPING
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.36,0:28:05.56,中文,,0,0,0,,早上好。\N{\rEng}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.56,0:28:06.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你好。 你好。\N{\rEng}Hi. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.64,0:28:08.96,中文,,0,0,0,,这些是她的新生婴儿......\N{\rEng}And these are her new babies...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.96,0:28:10.20,中文,,0,0,0,,哦。\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.20,0:28:13.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你很清醒。 你好。\N{\rEng}You're pretty awake. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.08,0:28:16.56,中文,,0,0,0,,..28 世界上最稀有的鸟类之一。\N{\rEng}..28 of one of the world's rarest birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.56,0:28:18.12,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿。 你好。\N{\rEng}Hey. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.12,0:28:21.04,中文,,0,0,0,,北方秃鹮。\N{\rEng}The northern bald ibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.04,0:28:23.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你真的很快就会爱上他们。\N{\rEng}You really quickly fall in love with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.52,0:28:25.00,中文,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳娜笑了\N{\rEng}KATHARINA LAUGHS
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.00,0:28:29.32,中文,,0,0,0,,400 多年前，它们在欧洲被猎杀至灭绝。\N{\rEng}They were hunted to extinction in Europe over 400 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.32,0:28:34.68,中文,,0,0,0,,这些小鸡出生在动物园里。\N{\rEng}These chicks were born in a zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.68,0:28:37.44,中文,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳娜的任务是教导他们\N{\rEng}Katharina's task is to teach them
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.44,0:28:40.40,中文,,0,0,0,,成为狂野、自由的鸟儿。\N{\rEng}to become wild, free birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.40,0:28:43.48,中文,,0,0,0,,对对对。 科姆。 科姆。\N{\rEng}Yes, yes, yes. Komm. Komm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:48.24,中文,,0,0,0,,为此，她必须让他们相信她是他们的母亲。\N{\rEng}To do that, she must convince them that she is their mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.24,0:28:51.12,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个称为印记的过程。\N{\rEng}It's a process called imprinting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.12,0:28:54.96,中文,,0,0,0,,当事情发生时，小鸡们绝对不能看到或听到\N{\rEng}While it's happening, the chicks must never see or hear
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.96,0:28:58.52,中文,,0,0,0,,除海伦娜之外的任何其他人，\N{\rEng}any other human except Helena,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.52,0:29:02.00,中文,,0,0,0,,她第二次成为宜必思寄养妈妈。\N{\rEng}who's an ibis foster mum for the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.00,0:29:05.92,中文,,0,0,0,,他们必须始终穿着相同的黄色衣服\N{\rEng}They must always wear identical yellow clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.92,0:29:10.20,中文,,0,0,0,,并一次又一次地重复同样的声音。\N{\rEng}and repeat the same noises again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.40,0:29:14.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我们模仿成年人发出的声音，就像……\N{\rEng}We mimic the sounds the adults make, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.08,0:29:16.16,中文,,0,0,0,,她的叫声沙哑\N{\rEng}SHE MAKES HOARSE CALL
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.16,0:29:17.88,中文,,0,0,0,,咕咕！\N{\rEng}Kkrukk!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.88,0:29:19.56,中文,,0,0,0,,咕咕！ 克鲁普。\N{\rEng}Kkrukk! Kklup.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.56,0:29:20.96,中文,,0,0,0,,克鲁普。 克鲁普。\N{\rEng}Kklup. Kklup.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.96,0:29:22.28,中文,,0,0,0,,克鲁普。\N{\rEng}Kklup.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.28,0:29:23.76,中文,,0,0,0,,但我还不太擅长做这件事！\N{\rEng}But I'm not good yet at doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.76,0:29:25.00,中文,,0,0,0,,他们笑了\N{\rEng}THEY LAUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.00,0:29:26.56,中文,,0,0,0,,晚安。\N{\rEng}Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.56,0:29:28.72,中文,,0,0,0,,当小鸡们睡着的时候，他们就在这里……\N{\rEng}They're here when the chicks fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.72,0:29:30.16,中文,,0,0,0,,睡得好。\N{\rEng}Sleep well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.92,0:29:35.00,中文,,0,0,0,,..以及他们醒来时看到的第一件事。\N{\rEng}..and the first thing they see when they awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.00,0:29:37.16,中文,,0,0,0,,早上好，华尔迪们！ 你好！\N{\rEng}Good morning, waldies! Hallo!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.16,0:29:40.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我们吃点东西吧？ 是的，我们吃饭吧。\N{\rEng}Let's have something to eat, shall we? Yes, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.12,0:29:43.68,中文,,0,0,0,,他们有点像每个人类婴儿。\N{\rEng}They're a bit like every human baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.68,0:29:46.40,中文,,0,0,0,,他们只需要一点一点的食物\N{\rEng}They just need their food bit by bit by bit
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.40,0:29:47.76,中文,,0,0,0,,整天。\N{\rEng}all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.76,0:29:49.68,中文,,0,0,0,,是的，是的，是的，是的，是的，是的。\N{\rEng}Yes, yes, yes, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.68,0:29:52.56,中文,,0,0,0,,哦，不，我们都做错了！\N{\rEng}Oh, no, we did it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.56,0:29:54.28,中文,,0,0,0,,哦！ 噢！\N{\rEng}Oh! Aw!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.28,0:29:56.84,中文,,0,0,0,,这真的就像给婴儿换尿布一样。\N{\rEng}It's really like changing the nappies of the babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.84,0:30:00.56,中文,,0,0,0,,28个嘴要喂，屁股要擦，\N{\rEng}28 mouths to feed and bottoms to wipe,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.56,0:30:03.60,中文,,0,0,0,,并一直与鸟儿交谈。\N{\rEng}and all the time talking to the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.60,0:30:05.96,中文,,0,0,0,,科姆，科姆，华尔迪！ 科姆，科姆！\N{\rEng}Komm, komm, waldies! Komm, komm!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.96,0:30:07.60,中文,,0,0,0,,感觉真的很累。\N{\rEng}Feeling really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.60,0:30:10.28,中文,,0,0,0,,是的，我真的很想多睡一会儿。\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'd really like to sleep a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.92,0:30:15.64,中文,,0,0,0,,几周过去了，两人之间的联系越来越紧密。\N{\rEng}As the weeks pass, the bond grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.64,0:30:18.56,中文,,0,0,0,,然后是他们下一阶段的时间了\N{\rEng}And then it is time for their next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.56,0:30:20.76,中文,,0,0,0,,成为野鸟。\N{\rEng}in becoming wild birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.00,0:30:28.52,中文,,0,0,0,,他们搬到了奥地利阿尔卑斯山的一块田地。\N{\rEng}They move to a field in the Austrian Alps.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.84,0:30:37.20,中文,,0,0,0,,它们现在已经长出了成年飞羽……\N{\rEng}They've now grown their adult flight feathers...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.68,0:30:41.40,中文,,0,0,0,,......但他们的内心仍然是小鸡。\N{\rEng}...but they're still chicks on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.72,0:30:45.60,中文,,0,0,0,,所以印记必须继续。\N{\rEng}So the imprinting must continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.60,0:30:48.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我们用这个手势，\N{\rEng}With this hand gesture we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.08,0:30:51.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我们模仿成年朱鹮的喙\N{\rEng}we imitate the bill of an adult ibis
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.12,0:30:53.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我们将它与问候声音结合起来。\N{\rEng}and we combine it with the greeting sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.08,0:30:54.32,中文,,0,0,0,,所以，这是...\N{\rEng}So, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.32,0:30:56.28,中文,,0,0,0,,克鲁普！ 克鲁普！\N{\rEng}Kklup! Kklup!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.28,0:31:01.36,中文,,0,0,0,,所有这些印记都有一个非常重要的原因。\N{\rEng}All this imprinting is for a very important reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.72,0:31:06.44,中文,,0,0,0,,这些是候鸟。\N{\rEng}These are migratory birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.44,0:31:09.08,中文,,0,0,0,,秋天，他们必须飞向南方\N{\rEng}In autumn, they must fly south
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.08,0:31:12.20,中文,,0,0,0,,到意大利温暖的觅食地。\N{\rEng}to their warm feeding grounds in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.32,0:31:16.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个问题。\N{\rEng}And that is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.08,0:31:19.56,中文,,0,0,0,,他们知道他们需要去某个地方\N{\rEng}They know that they need to go somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.56,0:31:23.08,中文,,0,0,0,,但他们不知道朝哪个方向、走多远。\N{\rEng}but they don't know in which direction and how far.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.08,0:31:26.44,中文,,0,0,0,,所以他们需要向父母学习路线。\N{\rEng}So they need to learn the route from their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.80,0:31:30.56,中文,,0,0,0,,他们的人类母亲必须为他们指明道路。\N{\rEng}Their human mothers must show them the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.32,0:31:35.48,中文,,0,0,0,,这需要一点聪明才智。\N{\rEng}And that requires a little ingenuity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.48,0:31:37.40,中文,,0,0,0,,发动机启动\N{\rEng}ENGINE POWERS UP
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.72,0:31:48.16,中文,,0,0,0,,这是对印记进行测试的地方。\N{\rEng}This is where the imprinting is put to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.16,0:32:00.40,中文,,0,0,0,,鸟儿会跟着他们吗...\N{\rEng}Will the birds follow them...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.88,0:32:03.84,中文,,0,0,0,,..即使在微光下？\N{\rEng}..even in a microlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.84,0:32:05.64,中文,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳娜: 嗯，嗯！\N{\rEng}KATHARINA: Komm, komm!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.64,0:32:07.60,中文,,0,0,0,,科姆，科姆，华尔迪！\N{\rEng}Komm, komm, waldies!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.60,0:32:09.32,中文,,0,0,0,,科姆，科姆！\N{\rEng}Komm, komm!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.04,0:32:20.44,中文,,0,0,0,,翻译:\N{\rEng}TRANSLATION:
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.00,0:32:26.80,中文,,0,0,0,,距离太近对鸟类和人类来说都是危险的。\N{\rEng}Getting too close is dangerous for both birds and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.80,0:32:38.48,中文,,0,0,0,,哦哦哦哦哦哦！\N{\rEng}Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.04,0:32:57.32,中文,,0,0,0,,在经历了一段摇摇欲坠的开始之后……\N{\rEng}After a wobbly start...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.72,0:33:00.84,中文,,0,0,0,,..最后他们安定下来。\N{\rEng}..at last they settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.52,0:33:09.24,中文,,0,0,0,,印记已经发挥作用了。\N{\rEng}The imprinting has worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.52,0:33:23.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的鸽子今天表现得很好。\N{\rEng}Our birds did very well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.16,0:33:33.48,中文,,0,0,0,,但他们最大的挑战还在后头。\N{\rEng}But their biggest challenge is still to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.96,0:33:41.04,中文,,0,0,0,,齐勒塔尔阿尔卑斯山。\N{\rEng}The Zillertal Alps.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.12,0:33:49.16,中文,,0,0,0,,由岩石和冰组成的长城。\N{\rEng}A great wall of rock and ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.16,0:34:00.60,中文,,0,0,0,,这将是最重要的航班\N{\rEng}It's going to be the most important flight
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.60,0:34:02.52,中文,,0,0,0,,他们年轻的生命。\N{\rEng}of their young lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.64,0:34:07.84,中文,,0,0,0,,这将把他们带到精疲力竭的边缘。\N{\rEng}It will take them to the very edge of exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.84,0:34:11.48,中文,,0,0,0,,许多幼鸟在第一次迁徙期间死亡。\N{\rEng}A lot of young birds die during their first migration.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.48,0:34:13.44,中文,,0,0,0,,他们还是那么缺乏经验。\N{\rEng}They are still so inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.44,0:34:18.64,中文,,0,0,0,,养母和飞行员也面临着危险。\N{\rEng}There's also danger for the foster mothers and the pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.00,0:34:24.28,中文,,0,0,0,,如果微灯出现问题，\N{\rEng}If there is a problem with the microlights,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.28,0:34:26.60,中文,,0,0,0,,没有安全的着陆点。\N{\rEng}there is no safe place to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.60,0:34:33.16,中文,,0,0,0,,为了获得足够的高度飞越这些山脉......\N{\rEng}To gain enough height to fly over these mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.52,0:34:39.68,中文,,0,0,0,,..他们必须找到称为热气流的上升气流。\N{\rEng}..they must find columns of rising air called thermals.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.52,0:34:46.72,中文,,0,0,0,,这些鸟通常会学习的技能\N{\rEng}A skill these birds would normally learn
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.72,0:34:49.24,中文,,0,0,0,,跟随他们的亲生母亲。\N{\rEng}by following their natural mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.56,0:34:57.12,中文,,0,0,0,,风声\N{\rEng}WIND WHISTLES
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.84,0:35:09.64,中文,,0,0,0,,需要专业的驾驶才能找到热气流。\N{\rEng}It takes expert piloting to find the thermals.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.16,0:35:20.52,中文,,0,0,0,,一旦在一内，\N{\rEng}Once within one,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.52,0:35:23.48,中文,,0,0,0,,这是动荡和不可预测的。\N{\rEng}it's turbulent and unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.88,0:35:46.28,中文,,0,0,0,,每一次，妈妈们都必须确保\N{\rEng}With every turn, the mothers must make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.28,0:35:49.12,中文,,0,0,0,,所有 28 只鸟都跟随。\N{\rEng}all 28 birds are following.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.48,0:36:15.24,中文,,0,0,0,,所有 28 只鸟都在这里。\N{\rEng}All 28 birds here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.80,0:36:19.84,中文,,0,0,0,,唷。\N{\rEng}Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.80,0:36:19.84,中文,,0,0,0,,她如释重负地笑了\N{\rEng}SHE LAUGHS IN RELIEF
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.60,0:36:36.32,中文,,0,0,0,,最后，他们翻越了最高的山脊。\N{\rEng}At last, they make it over the highest ridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.44,0:36:54.96,中文,,0,0,0,,从现在开始，飞行应该很容易。\N{\rEng}From now on, it should be easy flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.88,0:37:19.08,中文,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳娜:除了拯救朱鹮之外，我们正在努力做的事情\N{\rEng}KATHARINA: What we are trying to do, apart from saving the ibis,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.08,0:37:21.72,中文,,0,0,0,,正在努力给人们带来希望。\N{\rEng}is trying to give hope to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.12,0:37:27.20,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你能带回一种物种\N{\rEng}If you can bring back one species,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.20,0:37:29.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你也可以和其他人一起做。\N{\rEng}you can also do it with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.20,0:37:46.96,中文,,0,0,0,,曾经被遗弃的物种现在有了未来。\N{\rEng}A species once left for dead now has a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.56,0:37:54.16,中文,,0,0,0,,他们前往安全的冬季家园\N{\rEng}And they head for their safe winter home
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.16,0:37:56.88,中文,,0,0,0,,在一个受保护的自然保护区。\N{\rEng}in a protected nature reserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.12,0:38:19.72,中文,,0,0,0,,喇叭蜂鸣声\N{\rEng}HORN BEEPS
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.72,0:38:23.76,中文,,0,0,0,,但正如我们在本系列中所看到的，\N{\rEng}But as we have seen throughout this series,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.76,0:38:29.16,中文,,0,0,0,,许多物种正在失去生存所需的野生栖息地。\N{\rEng}many species are losing the wild habitats they need to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.80,0:38:35.88,中文,,0,0,0,,这是灭绝的最大原因。\N{\rEng}It's the biggest cause of extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.36,0:38:48.92,中文,,0,0,0,,这一点在亚马逊雨林中表现得最为明显。\N{\rEng}Nowhere is this more apparent than in the Amazon rainforest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.36,0:38:56.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的《地球脉动》剧组曾多次在这里拍摄\N{\rEng}Our Planet Earth crews have filmed here many times
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.12,0:38:58.72,中文,,0,0,0,,在过去的二十年里。\N{\rEng}over the last two decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.16,0:39:06.92,中文,,0,0,0,,木材嘎吱作响\N{\rEng}TIMBER CREAKING
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.92,0:39:12.64,中文,,0,0,0,,在那段时间里，超过 160 亿棵树......\N{\rEng}And in that time, over 16,000 million trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.68,0:39:16.72,中文,,0,0,0,,..已经被砍倒了。\N{\rEng}..have been felled.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.44,0:39:26.84,中文,,0,0,0,,为了保护生活在这里的无数物种......\N{\rEng}To safeguard the countless species that live here...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.84,0:39:29.48,中文,,0,0,0,,..森林本身必须受到保护..\N{\rEng}..the forest itself must be protected..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.88,0:39:36.48,中文,,0,0,0,,有一股力量正在兴起来做到这一点。\N{\rEng}And there's a force rising up to do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.84,0:39:40.96,中文,,0,0,0,,翻译:\N{\rEng}TRANSLATION:
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.48,0:40:07.24,中文,,0,0,0,,亚历山德拉·科拉普 (Alessandra Korap) 是蒙杜鲁库 (Munduruku) 的领导人之一。\N{\rEng}Alessandra Korap is one of the leaders of the Munduruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.00,0:40:12.48,中文,,0,0,0,,他们一直是亚马逊这片地区的守护者\N{\rEng}They have been the guardians of this part of the Amazon
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.48,0:40:15.04,中文,,0,0,0,,千百年来。\N{\rEng}for thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.44,0:40:57.32,中文,,0,0,0,,当她还是个孩子的时候，亚马逊森林的这一部分\N{\rEng}When she was a child, this part of the Amazon forest
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.32,0:41:01.12,中文,,0,0,0,,绵延数百英里，绵延不绝。\N{\rEng}stretched unbroken for hundreds of miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.84,0:41:10.36,中文,,0,0,0,,现在已经被瓜分了...\N{\rEng}Now it's being carved up...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.56,0:41:14.64,中文,,0,0,0,,..用于采矿、木材、\N{\rEng}..for mining, for timber,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.64,0:41:17.64,中文,,0,0,0,,但最重要的是农业。\N{\rEng}but most of all for agriculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.96,0:41:25.40,中文,,0,0,0,,这是亚马逊争夺战的前线，\N{\rEng}This is the front line in the battle for the Amazon,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.40,0:41:27.76,中文,,0,0,0,,这是致命的。\N{\rEng}and it is a deadly one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.96,0:41:36.48,中文,,0,0,0,,过去十年，超过300人被谋杀\N{\rEng}In the last decade, more than 300 people have been murdered
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.48,0:41:39.72,中文,,0,0,0,,在巴西保护环境。\N{\rEng}in Brazil defending the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.36,0:42:10.88,中文,,0,0,0,,蒙杜鲁库人，像许多土著群体一样，\N{\rEng}The Munduruku, like many indigenous groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.88,0:42:13.48,中文,,0,0,0,,生活在偏僻的社区\N{\rEng}live in isolated communities
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.48,0:42:18.04,中文,,0,0,0,,容易受到矿工、农民和伐木者的攻击。\N{\rEng}vulnerable to attack from miners, farmers and loggers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.92,0:42:49.64,中文,,0,0,0,,亚马逊河的未来就在 2,000 英里之外决定。\N{\rEng}The Amazon's future is decided 2,000 miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.72,0:42:55.52,中文,,0,0,0,,在这里，在巴西议会，\N{\rEng}Here, in the parliament of Brazil,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.52,0:42:59.36,中文,,0,0,0,,正在讨论允许剥削的新法律\N{\rEng}new laws are being debated to allow the exploitation
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.36,0:43:01.80,中文,,0,0,0,,他们的传统部落土地。\N{\rEng}of their traditional tribal land.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.68,0:43:10.28,中文,,0,0,0,,但亚历山德拉有一个计划--\N{\rEng}But Alessandra has a plan -
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.28,0:43:13.12,中文,,0,0,0,,与其他部落联合\N{\rEng}to unite with other tribes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.12,0:43:15.96,中文,,0,0,0,,并组织了如此大规模的抗议活动\N{\rEng}and organise a protest so big
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.96,0:43:18.56,中文,,0,0,0,,它不容忽视。\N{\rEng}that it cannot be ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.60,0:44:10.92,中文,,0,0,0,,这是前往首都的三天旅程。\N{\rEng}It's a three-day journey to the capital city.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.92,0:44:13.04,中文,,0,0,0,,喇叭声\N{\rEng}HORN BLARES
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.44,0:44:17.60,中文,,0,0,0,,卡车隆隆地进出田野……\N{\rEng}Trucks rumble to and from the fields...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.48,0:44:23.08,中文,,0,0,0,,..曾经是雨林的土地。\N{\rEng}..land that used to be rainforest.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.32,0:44:28.52,中文,,0,0,0,,他们正在运送数千吨大豆。\N{\rEng}They're carrying thousands of tonnes of soya beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.00,0:44:35.16,中文,,0,0,0,,它从亚马逊中心地带运往世界各地。\N{\rEng}It's shipped from the heart of the Amazon across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.04,0:44:39.72,中文,,0,0,0,,不是为了养活人类...\N{\rEng}Not to feed humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.72,0:44:41.80,中文,,0,0,0,,..但要喂养牲畜。\N{\rEng}..but to feed livestock.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.48,0:45:09.56,中文,,0,0,0,,最终，亚历山德拉抵达巴西利亚。\N{\rEng}Eventually, Alessandra makes it to Brasilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.04,0:45:14.76,中文,,0,0,0,,抗议的消息已经传遍全国。\N{\rEng}News of the protest has spread all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.48,0:45:22.12,中文,,0,0,0,,200个团体团结在一个巨大的营地里。\N{\rEng}200 groups have united in a huge camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.12,0:45:23.88,中文,,0,0,0,,抗议者唱歌\N{\rEng}PROTESTORS SING
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.88,0:45:29.16,中文,,0,0,0,,来自巴西东北部的Xukuru。\N{\rEng}From the northeast of Brazil - the Xukuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.88,0:45:34.28,中文,,0,0,0,,来自亚马逊南部边缘 - 卡拉贾。\N{\rEng}From the southern edge of the Amazon - the Karaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.64,0:45:50.28,中文,,0,0,0,,他们抗议拟议的法律长达十天。\N{\rEng}For ten days, they protest against the proposed laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.56,0:46:12.16,中文,,0,0,0,,亚历山德拉和其他领导人创造了\N{\rEng}Alessandra and the other leaders have created
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.16,0:46:17.00,中文,,0,0,0,,巴西有史以来最大规模的原住民抗议活动。\N{\rEng}the biggest protest by indigenous people ever held in Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.40,0:46:31.44,中文,,0,0,0,,后来，其中一项拟议的法律被撤回。\N{\rEng}Later, one of the proposed laws was withdrawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.20,0:46:39.96,中文,,0,0,0,,虽小但意义重大的胜利\N{\rEng}A small but significant victory
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.96,0:46:43.68,中文,,0,0,0,,亚历山德拉为巴西荒野而战。\N{\rEng}in Alessandra's fight for Brazil's wild places.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.04,0:46:56.36,中文,,0,0,0,,栖息地破坏是目前最大的威胁\N{\rEng}The destruction of habitats is currently the biggest threat
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.36,0:46:59.32,中文,,0,0,0,,为了动物物种的生存。\N{\rEng}to the survival of animal species.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.32,0:47:03.80,中文,,0,0,0,,但更大的灾难即将来临。\N{\rEng}But there is an even greater disaster on the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.80,0:47:06.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的气候正在发生变化。\N{\rEng}Our climate is changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.44,0:47:10.40,中文,,0,0,0,,季节变得不可预测且更加极端。\N{\rEng}Seasons have become unpredictable and more extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.40,0:47:13.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的星球正在变得越来越热。\N{\rEng}Our planet is getting hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.36,0:47:20.04,中文,,0,0,0,,科学家预测，如果全球气温升高\N{\rEng}Scientists predict that if the global temperature
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.04,0:47:22.80,中文,,0,0,0,,上升超过两度，\N{\rEng}rises by over two degrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.80,0:47:27.00,中文,,0,0,0,,它很可能成为灭绝的头号原因。\N{\rEng}it is likely to become the number one cause of extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.28,0:47:32.08,中文,,0,0,0,,为了阻止气候变化，\N{\rEng}To halt climate change,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.08,0:47:35.32,中文,,0,0,0,,也许政治家也需要成为英雄。\N{\rEng}perhaps politicians need to become heroes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.60,0:47:39.20,中文,,0,0,0,,记者:大家好，晚上好，热烈欢迎来到格拉斯哥\N{\rEng}REPORTER: Hello, good evening, and a warm welcome to Glasgow
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.20,0:47:42.40,中文,,0,0,0,,以及期待已久的气候峰会 COP26 的开始。\N{\rEng}and the start of the long-awaited climate summit, COP26.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.40,0:47:44.92,中文,,0,0,0,,世界领导人、杰出科学家\N{\rEng}World leaders, prominent scientists
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.92,0:47:47.24,中文,,0,0,0,,和顾问们都已准备好迎接 12 天的...\N{\rEng}and advisers all ready for 12 days of...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.24,0:47:49.88,中文,,0,0,0,,穆罕默德·纳希德是一位政治家，\N{\rEng}Mohamed Nasheed is a politician,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.88,0:47:53.00,中文,,0,0,0,,马尔代夫前总统。\N{\rEng}the former president of the Maldives.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.00,0:47:56.76,中文,,0,0,0,,穆罕默德:医生说他们拿走了 16 个滚珠轴承\N{\rEng}MOHAMED: The doctors said that they took 16 ball bearings
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.76,0:48:00.68,中文,,0,0,0,,来自我身体的各个部位。\N{\rEng}from all parts of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.68,0:48:03.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我昏迷了两天。\N{\rEng}I was unconscious for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.40,0:48:10.44,中文,,0,0,0,,在他的政治生涯中，他遭受过酷刑、监禁\N{\rEng}Over his political career, he has been tortured, imprisoned
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.44,0:48:14.08,中文,,0,0,0,,最近在一次暗杀行动中幸存下来。\N{\rEng}and recently survived an assassination attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.72,0:48:18.44,中文,,0,0,0,,但那段时间，\N{\rEng}But during that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.44,0:48:22.76,中文,,0,0,0,,他还不懈地与气候变化作斗争。\N{\rEng}he's also fought relentlessly against climate change.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.32,0:48:27.64,中文,,0,0,0,,..很高兴能够为您带来穆罕默德·纳希德。\N{\rEng}..pleasure to be able to bring you Mohamed Nasheed.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.64,0:48:29.56,中文,,0,0,0,,观众欢呼\N{\rEng}AUDIENCE CHEERS
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.56,0:48:34.04,中文,,0,0,0,,在格拉斯哥气候大会 COP26 召开前夕，\N{\rEng}In Glasgow, on the eve of climate conference COP26,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.04,0:48:35.92,中文,,0,0,0,,他正在一次集会上发表讲话。\N{\rEng}he is addressing a rally.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.92,0:48:37.52,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢。\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.52,0:48:39.44,中文,,0,0,0,,非常感谢。\N{\rEng}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.60,0:48:46.40,中文,,0,0,0,,所以，我们来到了 COP26\N{\rEng}So, we come to COP26
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.40,0:48:49.84,中文,,0,0,0,,看看我们是否还有未来。\N{\rEng}to find out whether we still have a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.84,0:48:54.36,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们无法达成具有法律约束力的协议\N{\rEng}If we cannot have a legally binding agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.36,0:48:58.36,中文,,0,0,0,,不要推高全球气温\N{\rEng}not to push global temperatures
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.36,0:49:00.88,中文,,0,0,0,,1.5度以上，\N{\rEng}above 1.5 degrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.88,0:49:03.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我的国家将会消失\N{\rEng}my country will be gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.44,0:49:06.04,中文,,0,0,0,,世界上所有的珊瑚礁也一样\N{\rEng}as will all the world's coral reefs
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.04,0:49:09.68,中文,,0,0,0,,和大部分雨林。\N{\rEng}and most of the rainforests.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.68,0:49:14.00,中文,,0,0,0,,这一切的破坏真的值得吗\N{\rEng}Is all this devastation really worth it,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.00,0:49:18.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这样我们就可以继续燃烧煤炭和化石燃料\N{\rEng}so that we can continue to burn coal and fossil fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.64,0:49:21.00,中文,,0,0,0,,再过几年？\N{\rEng}for a few more years?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.52,0:49:26.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我用了一生\N{\rEng}I have spent a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.56,0:49:28.96,中文,,0,0,0,,为我的国家而战，\N{\rEng}fighting for my country,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.96,0:49:31.96,中文,,0,0,0,,并以比以往更加坚定的决心，\N{\rEng}and with more determination than ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.96,0:49:36.56,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我知道我在地球上的时间可能会缩短。\N{\rEng}because I know my time on Earth might be cut short.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.68,0:49:40.96,中文,,0,0,0,,穆罕默德·纳希德对自然世界的热情\N{\rEng}Mohamed Nasheed's passion for the natural world
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.96,0:49:45.68,中文,,0,0,0,,开始于他第一次看到珊瑚礁。\N{\rEng}began the first time he saw a coral reef.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.92,0:50:00.08,中文,,0,0,0,,穆罕默德:我最早的记忆\N{\rEng}MOHAMED: My earliest memory
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.08,0:50:04.32,中文,,0,0,0,,与海洋和珊瑚礁在一起。\N{\rEng}is with the ocean and the reef.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.32,0:50:09.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我们是第一代真正看到珊瑚礁的人。\N{\rEng}We were the first generation to actually see the reef.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.88,0:50:13.36,中文,,0,0,0,,口罩和护目镜来到马尔代夫\N{\rEng}Masks and goggles came to the Maldives
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.36,0:50:16.04,中文,,0,0,0,,60年代末、70年代初。\N{\rEng}in the late '60s, early '70s.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.80,0:50:25.04,中文,,0,0,0,,一旦我们开始将珊瑚礁视为一个生物......\N{\rEng}Once we started seeing the reef as a living creature...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.04,0:50:28.72,中文,,0,0,0,,..我们只是傻眼了。\N{\rEng}..we were just dumbfounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.36,0:50:36.12,中文,,0,0,0,,但纳希德心爱的珊瑚现在成了栖息地\N{\rEng}But Nasheed's beloved coral is now the habitat
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.12,0:50:39.96,中文,,0,0,0,,这是受气候变化威胁最大的国家。\N{\rEng}that is most threatened by climate change.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.28,0:50:49.16,中文,,0,0,0,,临界临界点是温度升高 1.5 度。\N{\rEng}The critical tipping point is a 1.5 degree temperature rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.36,0:50:53.44,中文,,0,0,0,,除此之外，大多数珊瑚礁都会死亡，\N{\rEng}Beyond that, most reefs will die,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.44,0:50:56.44,中文,,0,0,0,,除了瓦砾什么也没有留下。\N{\rEng}leaving nothing but rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.20,0:51:01.92,中文,,0,0,0,,当你想到更大的图景时，\N{\rEng}When you think of a bigger picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.92,0:51:06.60,中文,,0,0,0,,那么你自己的生活就不那么重要了。\N{\rEng}then your own life is not so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.40,0:51:12.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这是你想要完成的事情，这很重要。\N{\rEng}It's what you want to get done which is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.24,0:51:19.36,中文,,0,0,0,,纳希德的目标是说服政客减少使用\N{\rEng}Nasheed's aim is to persuade politicians to cut the use
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.36,0:51:21.80,中文,,0,0,0,,煤炭和其他化石燃料。\N{\rEng}of coal and other fossil fuels.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.60,0:51:27.28,中文,,0,0,0,,他在每次气候会议上都会重复这一呼吁。\N{\rEng}He repeats this plea at every climate conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.28,0:51:29.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你需要能够说服人们，\N{\rEng}You need to be able to convince people,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.88,0:51:32.04,中文,,0,0,0,,尝试教育人们。\N{\rEng}try to educate people.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.04,0:51:33.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我们有麻烦了。\N{\rEng}We are in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.84,0:51:38.36,中文,,0,0,0,,如果地球温度超过 1.5 度，我们将无法生存。\N{\rEng}We will not survive if the planet is heated above 1.5 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.36,0:51:40.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须立即行动。\N{\rEng}We must act now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.56,0:51:44.84,中文,,0,0,0,,一开始，记者们正在报道一些引人注目的承诺\N{\rEng}At first, journalists are reporting on some eye-catching promises
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.84,0:51:47.00,中文,,0,0,0,,由国家元首制定。\N{\rEng}made by heads of state.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.00,0:51:49.64,中文,,0,0,0,,记者:18个国家已做出承诺\N{\rEng}REPORTER: 18 countries have committed themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.64,0:51:52.44,中文,,0,0,0,,停止使用燃煤发电厂的计划。\N{\rEng}to a plan to stop using coal-fired power plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.44,0:51:54.28,中文,,0,0,0,,现在这是一个选举问题。\N{\rEng}It is an election issue now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.28,0:51:57.96,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是世界领导人加入这一言论的原因。\N{\rEng}That is why world leaders have joined the rhetoric.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.96,0:52:03.68,中文,,0,0,0,,下一阶段--将承诺转化为切实的计划。\N{\rEng}The next stage - turning promises into solid plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.68,0:52:07.12,中文,,0,0,0,,而纳希德则忙于幕后工作。\N{\rEng}And Nasheed is busy working behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.12,0:52:10.08,中文,,0,0,0,,如果他们不同意，我们会打电话给他们的部长、总统\N{\rEng}If they don't agree, we will ring their ministers, their presidents
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.08,0:52:11.80,中文,,0,0,0,,并让他们上网。\N{\rEng}and get them online.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.80,0:52:13.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我认为这就是我们正在努力做的事情。\N{\rEng}I think that's what we're trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.92,0:52:15.76,中文,,0,0,0,,那么让我们这样做吧。\N{\rEng}So let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.36,0:52:18.92,中文,,0,0,0,,总理，你好吗？\N{\rEng}How are you, Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.92,0:52:20.16,中文,,0,0,0,,是的，好的。 我可以听见你，\N{\rEng}Yeah, OK. I can hear you,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.16,0:52:22.44,中文,,0,0,0,,但我能更清楚地听到总理的话。\N{\rEng}but I can hear the Prime Minister much clearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.44,0:52:25.80,中文,,0,0,0,,所有国家都需要就最终文本达成一致 -\N{\rEng}All countries need to agree to the final text -
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.80,0:52:28.04,中文,,0,0,0,,有些人不会。\N{\rEng}and some won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.04,0:52:31.48,中文,,0,0,0,,想要继续使用化石燃料的人们，\N{\rEng}People who want to continue fossil fuel,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.48,0:52:33.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我想，都是坏人。\N{\rEng}I think, are the bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.88,0:52:38.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得那些想要改变的人都是好人。\N{\rEng}And people who want to change, I feel, are the good guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.32,0:52:41.16,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢。 太感谢了。\N{\rEng}Thank you. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.76,0:52:46.64,中文,,0,0,0,,14 天后，本次 COP 结束...\N{\rEng}After 14 days, this COP closes...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.64,0:52:49.12,中文,,0,0,0,,..有了一些进展，\N{\rEng}..with some progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.12,0:52:52.32,中文,,0,0,0,,但也有很大的妥协。\N{\rEng}but also with big compromises.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.32,0:52:55.04,中文,,0,0,0,,新闻阅读器:今晚终于达成协议\N{\rEng}NEWSREADER: An agreement was finally reached this evening
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.04,0:52:57.48,中文,,0,0,0,,在关于煤炭未来使用的关键部分之后\N{\rEng}after a key section on the future use of coal
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.48,0:52:59.44,中文,,0,0,0,,在最后一刻被淡化了。\N{\rEng}was at the last moment watered down.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.04,0:53:04.44,中文,,0,0,0,,如果没有紧急的新承诺，\N{\rEng}Without urgent new commitments,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.44,0:53:07.92,中文,,0,0,0,,1.5度的目标将无法实现。\N{\rEng}the target of 1.5 degrees will be missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.92,0:53:09.92,中文,,0,0,0,,这是灾难性的。\N{\rEng}It is disastrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.92,0:53:11.44,中文,,0,0,0,,它会...\N{\rEng}It will...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.44,0:53:14.24,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你想象这个，如果你能理解它......\N{\rEng}If you picture this, if you can fathom it...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.84,0:53:20.76,中文,,0,0,0,,..珊瑚会白化\N{\rEng}..the coral will bleach
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.76,0:53:22.76,中文,,0,0,0,,他们将会死去，\N{\rEng}and they will die,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.76,0:53:24.92,中文,,0,0,0,,当他们死后，\N{\rEng}and when they are dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.92,0:53:29.40,中文,,0,0,0,,生活在那里的鱼和海洋生物......\N{\rEng}the fish and the marine life that lives there...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.40,0:53:31.60,中文,,0,0,0,,..不复存在。\N{\rEng}..cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.68,0:53:45.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你可能会认为你的正常首相\N{\rEng}You would have thought that your normal prime minister
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.96,0:53:47.64,中文,,0,0,0,,还有总统……\N{\rEng}and president...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.20,0:53:53.12,中文,,0,0,0,,..会更好地理解事物。\N{\rEng}..would have a better grip on understanding things.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.12,0:53:57.24,中文,,0,0,0,,不只是不断地继续\N{\rEng}And not just go on and on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.24,0:53:59.48,中文,,0,0,0,,关于保护他们的生活方式。\N{\rEng}about protecting their way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.24,0:54:06.36,中文,,0,0,0,,所以看到政客们真是令人沮丧……\N{\rEng}So it's frustrating to see politicians...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.60,0:54:10.16,中文,,0,0,0,,..谁似乎不明白。\N{\rEng}..who doesn't seem to understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.56,0:54:16.76,中文,,0,0,0,,就目前的政策来看，\N{\rEng}With current policies,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.76,0:54:20.16,中文,,0,0,0,,99%的珊瑚礁可能消失...\N{\rEng}99% of coral reefs could be gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.84,0:54:24.16,中文,,0,0,0,,..不到30年。\N{\rEng}..in under 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.44,0:54:28.12,中文,,0,0,0,,其他栖息地也会随之而来。\N{\rEng}Other habitats will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.40,0:54:34.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你不能失去希望。\N{\rEng}You can't lose hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.40,0:54:37.28,中文,,0,0,0,,你不能放弃。\N{\rEng}You cannot give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.68,0:54:40.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我不会停止。\N{\rEng}I will not stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.16,0:54:45.92,中文,,0,0,0,,纳希德相信有一个解决方案。\N{\rEng}Nasheed believes there is a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.64,0:54:53.64,中文,,0,0,0,,环境越成为选举问题，\N{\rEng}The more environment becomes an election issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.64,0:54:57.16,中文,,0,0,0,,将会有更多针对气候的行动。\N{\rEng}there will be more action on climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.64,0:55:03.08,中文,,0,0,0,,每次你投票，每次选举，\N{\rEng}Every time you vote, in every election,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.08,0:55:05.32,中文,,0,0,0,,请勾选这个星球。\N{\rEng}please tick the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.56,0:55:22.52,中文,,0,0,0,,拯救物种的挑战不能留给少数人\N{\rEng}The challenge of saving species can't be left to a few
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.52,0:55:27.00,中文,,0,0,0,,克服困难的英雄人物。\N{\rEng}heroic individuals working against the odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.00,0:55:29.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这是那些拥有强大权力的人\N{\rEng}It's those in positions of great power
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.64,0:55:32.24,中文,,0,0,0,,谁能发挥最大作用。\N{\rEng}who can make the most difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.24,0:55:38.12,中文,,0,0,0,,因此，最终，他们必须承担最大的责任。\N{\rEng}So, ultimately, it is they who must take the most responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.12,0:55:43.44,中文,,0,0,0,,也许我们的角色之一就是让他们承担责任。\N{\rEng}Perhaps one of our roles is to hold them to account.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.44,0:55:47.12,中文,,0,0,0,,对于许多物种来说，时间已经不多了，\N{\rEng}Time is running out for many species,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.12,0:55:51.24,中文,,0,0,0,,但我坚信如果现在做出正确的决定\N{\rEng}but I truly believe that if the right decisions are made now,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.24,0:55:53.68,中文,,0,0,0,,在这个关键时刻，\N{\rEng}at this critical moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.68,0:55:57.20,中文,,0,0,0,,所有生命仍可能有光明的未来\N{\rEng}there could still be a bright future for all life
